{{Infobox football biography |name = Abdallahi Mahmoud |image = |image_size = |caption = |fullname = |birth_date = {{birth date and age|2000|5|4|df=y}} |birth_place = |height = |position = [[Defender (association football)|Defender]] |currentclub = [[Deportivo Alavés B]] |clubnumber = |years1 = 2018– |clubs1 = [[Deportivo Alavés B]] |caps1 = |goals1 = |nationalyears1 = 2018– |nationalteam1 = [[Mauritania national football team|Mauritania]] |nationalcaps1 = 1 |nationalgoals1 = 0 |club-update = 08:30, 5 October 2018 (UTC) |ntupdate = 08:30, 5 October 2018 (UTC) }} '''Abdallahi Mahmoud''' (born 4 May 2000) is a Mauritanian international [[association football|footballer]] who plays for [[Deportivo Alavés B]], as a [[Defender (association football)|defender]].
==Career== He has played club football for [[Deportivo Alavés B]].<ref name = "NFT">{{NFT player|id=71861|accessdate=5 October 2018}}</ref>
He made his international debut for [[Mauritania national football team|Mauritania]] in 2018.<ref name = "NFT"/>
