'''Chinese Taipei Athletics Association''' ('''CTAA'''; {{zh|c=中華民國田徑協會}}) is an [[IAAF]] recognised member officially representing [[Taiwan]]. The current president is [[Thomas Tsai]], and the general secretary is [[Wang Ching-cheng]]. The office is based in the building of Taiwan Sports Administration in Taipei City.

