The '''Estadio Centenario''' is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] built in 1988 in [[Armenia, Colombia]]. It is currently used mainly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home stadium of [[Deportes Quindío]]. The capacity is 20,716.<ref>http://es.fifa.com/mm/document/footballdevelopment/technicalsupport/01/52/19/97/fu20wcreportv2.pdf</ref>
