'''GFA Football Club''' is a Burmese [[association football|football]] club, based at [[Chin State]], [[Myanmar]]. The team was promoted to [[Myanmar National League]] in 2014, a year after its establishment. The club is one of the two teams representing Chin State.At the end of 2016 MNL-2, they promoted to MNL again.

