'''Malkiya SCC''' ({{Lang-ar|نادي المالكية}}) is a [[Bahrain]]i [[football (soccer)|football]] club based in [[Malkiya, Bahrain|Malkiya]]. They play in the top division in Bahraini football.

The club share the [[Madinat 'Isa Stadium]] with [[Al-Najma]].

Malkiya Club after 49 years, Since the establishment of this team, Became the champion of the [[Bahraini Premier League]] in [[2016–17 Bahrain First Division League|2017]].<ref>[http://www.goalzz.com/main.aspx?c=13187]</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gdnonline.com/Details/204691/Malkiya-crowned-champions|title=Malkiya crowned champions|publisher=Gulf Daily Online|date=14 May 2017}}</ref>

==Achievements==
