'''Polícia de Segurança Pública''' ([[Traditional Chinese]]: 警察) is a [[Macau|Macanese]] [[football (soccer)|football]] team which currently competes in the [[Liga de Elite]].

==Achievements==
*'''[[Campeonato da 1ª Divisão do Futebol|Macau Championship]]: 3'''
:: 1973, 2000, 2005

