'''Stade Municipal''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Bingerville]], [[Côte d'Ivoire]].  It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches. It serves as a home ground of [[Entente Sportive de Bingerville]]. The stadium holds 4,000 people.

